rows.label: qst100201_msg0001
rows.name:
You what? We already won the
auction for this, mate!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0002
rows.name:
Is there some kinda
misunderstanding here?
The successful bid was ours.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0003
rows.name: Ah ya ya...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0004
qst100201_msg0005
rows.name:
Hold your horses, you Superbian
drongo! You tryin' to pillage
me like you did to poor Gula?

rows.label: qst100201_msg0006
rows.name: Mo mo mo...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0007
rows.name:
What slander is this? Gula Province
was subject to a peaceful and mutually
beneficial transfer of power.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0008
rows.name:
...What am I saying? You Invidian
gobshites aren't capable of
understanding these things.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0009
rows.name:
Oh you're askin' to go home
on a bloody stretcher, mate!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0010
rows.name: Mo mo mo! Bashyfight is not allowed!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0011
rows.name: This Avaritia! Leave quarrels at home!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0012
rows.name:
Well how d'you propose we solve this
little problem then, Hiyaya mate?

rows.label: qst100201_msg0013
rows.name:
The auction was run by the
Avaritia Trade Guild. Maybe
it's their problem.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0014
rows.name: Ah ya ya... That...no...Hiyaya means...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0015
rows.name:
Ahh! Drivers! Helpppp! Help me!
Bashyfight! Hiyaya in danger!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0016
rows.name:
These men bid same amount for
special showcase Delta Vessel.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0017
rows.name:
But only one in stock...
They start to fight!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0018
rows.name:
Hang on a second there mate. If
there was only one in stock,
why did you accept two bids?

rows.label: qst100201_msg0019
rows.name:
Ah...ha... That was
Hiyaya's oversight...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0020
rows.name:
Well we've been fair messed around
thanks to your little "oversight". I'd
like to know how you intend to fix it.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0021
rows.name:
Ah ya ya... If only stock had
one more Delta Vessel...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0022
rows.name: Mo mo! Can friends fetch Delta Vessel?

rows.label: qst100201_msg0023
rows.name: Hiyaya will be eternally grateful...

rows.label: qst100201_msg0024
rows.name:
Friends can definitely find
Delta Vessel by salvaging
depths of Cloud Sea.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0025
rows.name:
Need to dive deeply! Here
is Hiyaya's favorite Special
Cylinder (Prov.).

rows.label: qst100201_msg0026
rows.name:
Please hurry before Hiyaya
become smash to bits by
angry customer friends.

rows.label: qst100201_msg0101
rows.name:
Please bring Delta Vessel
as fast as possible!

rows.label: qst100201_msg0102
rows.name: Fate of Hiyaya is in your hands!
